OL,3,CHoneymoon couple 'terrified' after
OL,4,CDubai hotel shook by missile strike
OL,6,FA couple from Liverpool have spoken of
OL,7,Ftheir panic after their hotel in Dubai
OL,8,Fwas hit in a missile strike
OL,10,FA couple on honeymoon in Dubai have
OL,11,Ftold ITV News they were terrified they
OL,12,Fwould "never see their family again"
OL,13,Fafter explosions shook their hotel
OL,14,Ffollowing a missile strike.
OL,16,FMatthew McGinn and Layla Hamood from
OL,17,FLiverpool are on holiday with their
OL,18,Fthree-year-old son Jenson, when the
OL,19,FFairmont Palm Hotel was struck.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
