CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772499776
OL,3,CHoneymoon couple 'terrified' after
OL,4,CDubai hotel shook by missile strike
OL,6,FThe family arrived in the United Arab
OL,7,FEmirates (UAE) in Dubai on Friday
OL,8,Fmorning, 27 February, and say they
OL,9,Fhave been 'terrified' to leave their
OL,10,Fhotel room since strikes launched by
OL,11,Fthe US and Israel on Saturday morning.
OL,13,FMatthew said they were having the
OL,14,F"best day" before the missile strike.
OL,16,FHe said: "We went downstairs to book a
OL,17,Frestaurant, before heading up to the
OL,18,Froom.
OL,20,F"Then we just heard this massive
OL,21,Fbang...the room shook."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772499776
OL,3,CHoneymoon couple 'terrified' after
OL,4,CDubai hotel shook by missile strike
OL,6,F"I can't describe the noise that I
OL,7,Fheard last night at around 3am...it
OL,8,Fwas like a really low-flying aircraft
OL,9,Fjust constantly above us.
OL,11,F"The noises are terrifying."
OL,13,FMatthew said: "It was probably panic
OL,14,Fmaking those phone calls, but we
OL,15,Fdidn't know if or when the next
OL,16,Fmissile would come."
OL,18,F"We're on edge and anxious right now,
OL,19,Fand this is two days after."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
