OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772499776
OL,3,CHoneymoon couple 'terrified' after
OL,4,CDubai hotel shook by missile strike
OL,6,FLayla, who was in the shower at the
OL,7,Ftime of the explosion, said she was
OL,8,F"in denial".
OL,10,FLayla said: "From our balcony we saw
OL,11,Fpeople on the floor, one of them was
OL,12,Fscreaming, so I knew we just had to
OL,13,Fget out."
OL,15,FDubai is a popular holiday destination
OL,16,Ffor Brits, and there are thousands of
OL,17,FBritish expats in the UAE.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
