OL,3,CHoneymoon couple 'terrified' after
OL,4,CDubai hotel shook by missile strike
OL,6,FIran fired missiles at its Gulf
OL,7,Fneighbours after the US and Israel
OL,8,Flaunched airstrikes on major cities,
OL,9,Fincluding the capital, Tehran, on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,12,FIran's Supreme Leader, Ali Khamenei,
OL,13,Fwas later confirmed to have died in
OL,14,Fthe assault.
OL,16,FFlights to and from countries in the
OL,17,FMiddle East are to remain suspended
OL,18,Funtil Monday as the conflict in the
OL,19,Fregion continues, major airlines have
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
