PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772499776
OL,3,CHoneymoon couple 'terrified' after
OL,4,CDubai hotel shook by missile strike
OL,6,FMatthew and Layla say they're "on
OL,7,Fedge" for any noises like a door
OL,8,Fslamming, have no idea whether they
OL,9,Fare safer indoors or outdoors.
OL,11,FThe couple are now waiting to find out
OL,12,Fwhen they can be rebooked on a flight
OL,13,Fhome.
OL,15,FThe Foreign Office has advised British
OL,16,Fnationals in Bahrain, Israel,
OL,17,FPalestine, Qatar and United Arab
OL,18,FEmirates to register their presence
OL,19,Fwith the UK Government to receive
OL,20,Fupdates on the situation in the Middle
OL,21,FEast.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
