PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772499776
OL,3,CHoneymoon couple 'terrified' after
OL,4,CDubai hotel shook by missile strike
OL,6,FIn a statement published on X on
OL,7,FSaturday night, the Foreign,
OL,8,FCommonwealth and Development Office
OL,9,F(FCDO) said: "British nationals in
OL,10,FBahrain, Israel, Palestine, Qatar and
OL,11,FUnited Arab Emirates can register
OL,12,Ftheir presence to receive direct
OL,13,Fupdates from the FCDO on the situation
OL,14,Fin the Middle East.
OL,16,F"You should continue to follow travel
OL,17,Fadvice and the advice of the local
OL,18,Fauthorities."
OL,26,@qD@NOUxD@AOUzD@MO]
